<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 13:01:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>摘要： 骨科及</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/abstract-department-of-orthopaedic-surgery-and</link><description>2&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/abstract156.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 13:01:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/abstract-department-of-orthopaedic-surgery-and</guid></item><item><title>摘要：美国佛罗里达州杰克逊维尔梅奥诊所肾内科和高血压科</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/abstract-division-of-nephrology-and-hypertension-mayo-clinic-jacksonville-florida-usa</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 12:46:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/abstract-division-of-nephrology-and-hypertension-mayo-clinic-jacksonville-florida-usa</guid></item><item><title>新发现的“死亡足迹”可能有助于病毒传播</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/newly-discovered-footprint-of-death-may-help-viruses-spread</link><description>我们体内发生的细胞搅动是巨大的，有数千亿个细胞&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/newly-discovered-footprint-of-death-may-help-viruses-spread.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 12:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/newly-discovered-footprint-of-death-may-help-viruses-spread</guid></item><item><title>在婴儿能够听到声音之前，他们的大脑就已经建立了接收声音的线路</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/before-babies-can-hear-their-brains-are-already-wiring-for-sound</link><description>约翰·霍普金斯大学的最新研究表明，早在婴儿的耳朵发挥功能之前，大脑就已经在构建听力所需的电路。发表于期刊&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/before-babies-can-hear-their-brains-are-already-wiring-for-sound2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 12:16:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/before-babies-can-hear-their-brains-are-already-wiring-for-sound</guid></item><item><title>研究发现免疫细胞相互作用的破坏是衰老的关键驱动因素</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/breakdown-of-immune-cells-interaction-is-key-driver-in-aging-study-finds</link><description>我们的衰老速度可能不同，但没有人能逃脱衰老。斯坦福大学医学院的研究人员对小鼠和人类细胞进行的一项研究将大部分责任归咎于特定类型的免疫细胞随着年龄的增长越来越无力吞噬另一种免疫细胞类型。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/breakdown-of-immune-cells-interaction-is-key-driver-in-aging-study-finds.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 12:01:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/breakdown-of-immune-cells-interaction-is-key-driver-in-aging-study-finds</guid></item><item><title>研究人员发现免疫细胞可以在肿瘤内建立抗癌中心</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/researchers-identify-immune-cell-that-builds-cancer-fighting-hubs-inside-tumors</link><description>西奈山伊坎医学院的研究人员发现了一种免疫细胞，它充当肿瘤内部形成的强大免疫中枢的建筑师和协调员，并在抗肿瘤免疫中发挥关键作用。这一发现可能会带来使癌症免疫疗法更加有效的新策略。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/researchers-identify-immune-cell-that-builds-cancer-fighting-hubs-inside-tumors.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 11:46:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/researchers-identify-immune-cell-that-builds-cancer-fighting-hubs-inside-tumors</guid></item><item><title>耳鸣严重程度的新“隐藏在视线中”的面部和眼部生物标志物可以打开测试治疗的道路</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/new-hidden-in-plain-sight-facial-and-eye-biomarkers-for-tinnitus-severity-could-unlock-path-to-testing-treatments</link><description>麻省总医院布里格姆分校的研究人员发现了耳鸣的新型生物标志物，这些生物标志物反映了神经系统的“战斗、逃跑或冻结”反应，并且可以通过拍摄患者聆听不愉快的声音来收集。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-hidden-in-plain-sight-facial-and-eye-biomarkers-for-tinnitus-severity-could-unlock-path-to-testing-treatments.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 11:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/new-hidden-in-plain-sight-facial-and-eye-biomarkers-for-tinnitus-severity-could-unlock-path-to-testing-treatments</guid></item><item><title>磁场可以帮助对抗帕金森病吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/can-magnetic-fields-help-fight-parkinsons-disease</link><description>一个国际团队成功地利用磁场来瞄准大脑深处的结构。研究人员将磁性纳米血小板注入相关区域。通过这样做，他们成功地治疗了患有帕金森病样症状的小鼠的运动缺陷。与目前用于治疗某些帕金森病患者的使用植入电极的标准刺激程序相比，新方法的侵入性较小。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/can-magnetic-fields-help-fight-parkinsons-disease.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 11:16:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/can-magnetic-fields-help-fight-parkinsons-disease</guid></item><item><title>一些代理人工智能浏览器可能存在重大网络安全风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/some-agentic-ai-browsers-may-come-with-major-cybersecurity-risks</link><description>在过去一年左右的时间里，人工智能公司推出了大量配备人工智能代理的网络浏览器。用户可能会要求这些代理之一计划假期，它将打开浏览器选项卡来研究路线和餐厅，然后进行预订并将活动添加到用户的日历中。其中任何一项的效果各不相同。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/some-agentic-ai-browsers-may-come-with-major-cybersecurity-risks.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 11:01:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/some-agentic-ai-browsers-may-come-with-major-cybersecurity-risks</guid></item><item><title>长期新冠病毒可能会损害大脑的多巴胺系统，从而影响动机和记忆力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/long-covid-may-affect-motivation-and-memory-by-injuring-the-brains-dopamine-system</link><description>了解新的脑部扫描如何将长期新冠肺炎与多巴胺系统的变化联系起来，这可能有助于解释疲劳、脑雾和动力丧失。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/long-covid-may-affect-motivation-and-memory-by-injuring-the-brains-dopamine-system.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 10:46:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/long-covid-may-affect-motivation-and-memory-by-injuring-the-brains-dopamine-system</guid></item></channel></rss>